<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Access Key - Secure Forum</title>
  <%- include('styles') %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>✅ Account Created Successfully!</h1>
    
    <div class="success-box">
      <p>
        <strong>Your account has been created.</strong> Below is your unique access key.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 2px solid #ffc107; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
      <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #856404;">
        Your Access Key:
      </label>
      <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #333; letter-spacing: 2px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #ffc107;">
        <%= userKey %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="error-box" style="background-color: #f8d7da; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;">
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #721c24;">
        <strong>⚠️ Important Security Notice:</strong><br><br>
        • Save this key in a secure location immediately<br>
        • This key will not be shown again<br>
        • You need this key to post comments<br>
        • Keep it private and secure<br>
        • Anyone with this key can post as you
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        Go to Forum
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
